                    "frequency": "Low",
                    "semantic_group_id": "1",
                    "name_type": "no",
                    "examples": [
                        {
                            "text": "In this context, you are using the word rather than just <w>mentioning</w> it."
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Philosophers often distinguish between using a term and <w>mentioning</w> it."
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
